Author: cjmoles
Title: Cash Poker Pro ICO- decentralized poker room
Body: Why buy more?  Buy more token from a shady project ---> that doesn't make sense at all.  I get into these things because I want to support projects that have potential, not because I like collecting senseless assets from platforms trying to collect a quick buck before they cut and run.  No, I'm not investing more into a project that has already proven to be incompetent because that belies reason.  There are much better projects available which could use some support.

Author: cjmoles

Body: Well, maybe it's actually your loss.  I've been doing this a long time and I can tell you that the more you invest in projects that have shady beginnings ---> the more you will lose in the long run.  There are projects out there that are going straight up and the more you put into projects that are tanking, the less you have to invest in the projects which are producing 10x - 100x gains.  Good luck ---> chasing bad money with good money is a terrible decision.

Author: Tactic
Title: Cash Poker Pro ICO- decentralized poker room
Body: Cash Poker Pro platform features    1. Players will play directly from their crypto wallets. No need to deposit money on poker room account. Thus, nobody can block your account and your money. No need for cash out transactions approval. 2. No charges, no fees and etc. Playing poker on-line can cost up to 40% of deposited amount of money for poker room owners and players at the end (10% bank commission for cash in and out, income tax, Gambling License fee, corporate taxes, Appstore charges and etc.) 3. No need to download any software and apps. Players can play directly from an internet link including popular messengers — facebook, telegram watsapp with huge auditory. 4. PRNG is 100% based on block chain. Players will love that nobody can influence cards come out. 5. Savings on operation cost as mentioned in clause 2 above will make games (rake) much cheaper. 6. Once you play poker using CASH you earning dividends at the same time, cause you are a token holder. 7. 100% anonymous game and token transactions. 8. The platform can not be blocked or prosecuted be any government as its based on a decentralized blockchain technology. More markets and players can join it. 9. Being a CASH token holder means to have an opportunity to have your own poker room as a profitable business. 10. All income generated by Cash Poker Pro platform is fairly divided between CASH token holders.

Author: CashPokerPro
Title: Cash Poker Pro ICO- decentralized poker room
Body: The mission of our project is to create a decentralized online poker room where users can trust. In today's online casino and poker sites use a centralized random number generator (RNG) , which is influenced from the outside. For example, the owner of the resource can influence on the process and the outcome of the game, have access to the server and the software code. This system causes distrust from users. Cheating with cards or the "bloody hand" in card games is often mentioned. Decentralized system and Blockchain technology can solve this problem.

Author: CashPokerPro
Title: Cash Poker Pro ICO- decentralized poker room
Body: Cash Poker Pro is a modern decentralized poker room with a network structure and a mechanism for fast and confidential money transfers based on the blockchain technology WhitePaper: http://cashpokerpro.io/whitepaper.pdf  ICO website: http://cashpokerpro.io   The project team is in gambling and entertainment industry for more than 10 years, and has more than 3 years of experience developing software for electronic poker tables. It has realized successfully some projects for electronic poker tables, bingo, online casinos.  The mission of our project is to create a decentralized online poker room where users can trust. In today's online casino and poker sites use a centralized random number generator (RNG) , which is influenced from the outside. For example, the owner of the resource can influence on the process and the outcome of the game, have access to the server and the software code. This system causes distrust from users. Cheating with cards or the "bloody hand" in card games is often mentioned. Decentralized system and Blockchain technology can solve this problem.  Along with the trust of users, the project is competitive due to the rapid and anonymous trasfers. You don't have to enter all your passport information at check-in and wait for weeks for your winnings!   We plan ICO in two steps. Everyone can use tokens CASH with the online poker room to play with other players and then exchange for Bitcoins, Esters or Fiat. In addition, all owners of the token will receive the dividends collected from each Bank. The Commission of the poker room (the rack) is from 1 to 5%, which will be distributed among investors minus the operating costs of the platform.  A total of 100 million Cash Poker Pro tokens (CASH) will be issued.  ICO will be held in several steps:  1. Pre-sale (26 of August 2017). At the step of the Pre-sale will be sold 10 million CASH. Cap - $500,000. The cost of 1 CASH = $0.05 Funds raised will benefit the implementation of global marketing strategies Cash Poker Pro and on the research and development and conducting advertising companies ICO project.  2. ICO (26th of October 2017).  ICO will be sold for 60 million in CASH.  The raised funds will go to develop its own blockchain for Ethereum code base, the development of the poker room, the massive advertising campaign of the poker room. Cash Poker Pro will accept tokens, CASH as game currency, with which you will be able to play with other players or exchange for other cryptocurrencies.  Join us in the Telegram. Subscribe to news on http://cashpokerpro.io
